715309f-a.title: Manhattan: 124th Street (East) - Park Avenue
715309f-a.text:
1O1-127 East 124th Street, at, adjoining, and east of the N.E. corner of Park Avenue. The one-story buildings in the foreground are the J. M. Horton Ice Cream Company. In the centre is the
rear of Proctor's 125th Street Theatre.
July 244, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
